{"hc3b2201dg2bd5g4fbaga447g69bfdeb79443": ["They'll suffer - whoever hurt Auntie will suffer.", "d7707fd3-301b-49a3-b7f1-2fb92cfa9805", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim3.html", "03e3cbb7-66e2-c663-f6c7-2af54d954e76"], "h2447aca5gf607g49d7g8ef4gda1143cf4774": ["Somebody hurt Auntie - I'll open their veins.", "d7707fd3-301b-49a3-b7f1-2fb92cfa9805", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim3.html", "d2cb9f4e-617e-3b45-bc0a-2cae8b7f129d"], "heab1c331g8509g49c6ga46dg7ee9a6a4754a": ["That mask is warping your mind - I need to remove it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim3.html", "7d4aba3a-c8c4-4174-d552-c5f9ce224cb4"], "hb3e6c6b9ge3fag45a9g8eecgc0ca90512f05": ["You can't take Auntie's gift! I won't let you!", "d7707fd3-301b-49a3-b7f1-2fb92cfa9805", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim3.html", "ba8d306b-452c-3af2-0ace-d5cba047a77f"], "hd8b8df4eg57a6g4476gb078g2f586ac4e0b6": ["The hag's dead - you're free now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim3.html", "cede5d70-f108-e451-9ab6-c81444d75f34"], "hd81b2ee2gc56cg4dedg922eg11791617bd95": ["I'll tear your throat out!", "d7707fd3-301b-49a3-b7f1-2fb92cfa9805", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim3.html", "c07b8cea-4e64-aa0f-5622-bdb71b955649"], "hbd3d533bgb4e9g4bb7g8445g40e0cbbc425f": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim3.html", "7eedb5a1-045d-c930-0d39-55fb4c93bafd"], "hf6ab1f4agb030g4d27g93abg960ec50cff78": ["Auntie will be awake soon. She'll be so angry.", "d7707fd3-301b-49a3-b7f1-2fb92cfa9805", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim3.html", "fcb63dbe-12ad-252b-237c-6af493cdae4b"], "h789e57e4g1682g4a45gaa03g351906f78b7e": ["If you hurt Auntie, I'll cut out your eyes.", "d7707fd3-301b-49a3-b7f1-2fb92cfa9805", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim3.html", "ff1035fa-6772-f540-fbd1-6924f